sources.description:
THE VICIOUS PAROLE RACKET... EXPOSED AT LAST... Convict's Code
On parole after three years in prison, a football player encounters the man who had framed him.
A man is framed and sent to prison for a crime he didn't commit. After three years in prison, when he is let out on limited parole, he sets out to clear his name and find the real criminals

Original title: Convict's Code (1939)
Directed by Lambert Hillyer

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/DFkrosnBWz4
